title: Looking for 5-man for youtube.

embed.description: Please LIKE & SUBSCRIBE! Help me reach 100 subs! Surprisingly, this one was probably one of my faster edits, yet the quality is better than any of the others, I've really picked up premiere pro.

body:
I've just started out on youtube, and my editing skills are rapidly increasing, which in turn, means I'm running out of source material relatively quickly. 

I have an account in plat 5, and silver 5, so I can queue with practically anyone. Looking for people with similar humour, and with no social life so they can play practically 24/7

I Already told you to add me and we'll do a colab lol
